---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Sobre">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-java-orange">JUG Joinville</h1>
    <div class="prose prose-invert">
      <p class="mb-6">
        The Java User Group Joinville (JUG Joinville) is a community-driven organization dedicated to
        bringing together Java developers, architects, and enthusiasts in the Joinville region.
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-java-blue">Our Mission</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        We aim to promote knowledge sharing, professional development, and networking opportunities
        within the Java ecosystem. Through regular meetups, workshops, and online events, we create a
        platform for learning and collaboration.
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-java-blue">Get Involved</h2>
      <p class="mb-6">
        Whether you're a seasoned Java developer or just starting your journey, there's a place for you
        in our community. Join our events, contribute to discussions, and connect with fellow Java
        enthusiasts.
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-java-blue">Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        Have questions or want to contribute? Reach out to us through our social media channels or join
        our Discord server.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>